  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a petty wizard in a small town. However, on the first day at your school, you step through its grand gates—only to uncover an unexpected truth. What does this revelation mean? Where will your curiosity lead you? What mysteries lie hidden beyond the familiar halls of your new school?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449950/extras/dbb20a7cebec2e9f88d3921041f7f734.poster.avif?t=1746097092\" width=614 height=153 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449950/extras/dbb20a7cebec2e9f88d3921041f7f734.webm?t=1746097092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Unravel the Truth Through Your Choices</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your life is not confined to classrooms. As you venture beyond its walls, you will witness strange events and meet all kinds of people. Along the way, countless choices await—each decision shaping the fate of those around you. Choose wisely, for your actions will carve the path ahead.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449950/extras/878d6e1914f7b98a6796e5af8bc5690e.poster.avif?t=1746097092\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449950/extras/878d6e1914f7b98a6796e5af8bc5690e.webm?t=1746097092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Grow Through Exploration and Battle</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The forest, the ocean, the mountain, and the snowland—each region is home to creatures that thrive in their unique environments. Defeat monsters, gather valuable resources, and craft essential items. The materials you obtain can be sold for gold or used to unlock new skills.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449950/extras/b9f40d5b8c1e90d6c6e04598fe361b43.poster.avif?t=1746097092\" width=614 height=153 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449950/extras/b9f40d5b8c1e90d6c6e04598fe361b43.webm?t=1746097092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Help Those in Need</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The quest board near the school is filled with requests from villagers and fellow students. Lend them a hand, and you'll be rewarded handsomely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449950/extras/9567d6484507dbc582913c3ff16162da.apng?t=1746097092\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449950/extras/9567d6484507dbc582913c3ff16162da.poster.avif?t=1746097092\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=153 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Craft, Discover, and Expand Your Knowledge</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine various materials to create new items and record your discoveries in the dictionary. Will you be able to collect and document every item hidden in the world?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449950/extras/8917802472a00bff60dd4af15f255859.apng?t=1746097092\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449950/extras/8917802472a00bff60dd4af15f255859.poster.avif?t=1746097092\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=153 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Tend to Your Own Farm</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow crops and harvest them with care. Your bounty can be used to learn new skills and craft powerful items.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a petty wizard in a small town. However, on the first day at your school, you step through its grand gates—only to uncover an unexpected truth. What does this revelation mean? Where will your curiosity lead you? What mysteries lie hidden beyond the familiar halls of your new school?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449950/extras/dbb20a7cebec2e9f88d3921041f7f734.poster.avif?t=1746097092\" width=614 height=153 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449950/extras/dbb20a7cebec2e9f88d3921041f7f734.webm?t=1746097092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Unravel the Truth Through Your Choices</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your life is not confined to classrooms. As you venture beyond its walls, you will witness strange events and meet all kinds of people. Along the way, countless choices await—each decision shaping the fate of those around you. Choose wisely, for your actions will carve the path ahead.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449950/extras/878d6e1914f7b98a6796e5af8bc5690e.poster.avif?t=1746097092\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449950/extras/878d6e1914f7b98a6796e5af8bc5690e.webm?t=1746097092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Grow Through Exploration and Battle</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The forest, the ocean, the mountain, and the snowland—each region is home to creatures that thrive in their unique environments. Defeat monsters, gather valuable resources, and craft essential items. The materials you obtain can be sold for gold or used to unlock new skills.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449950/extras/b9f40d5b8c1e90d6c6e04598fe361b43.poster.avif?t=1746097092\" width=614 height=153 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449950/extras/b9f40d5b8c1e90d6c6e04598fe361b43.webm?t=1746097092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Help Those in Need</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The quest board near the school is filled with requests from villagers and fellow students. Lend them a hand, and you'll be rewarded handsomely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449950/extras/9567d6484507dbc582913c3ff16162da.apng?t=1746097092\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449950/extras/9567d6484507dbc582913c3ff16162da.poster.avif?t=1746097092\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=153 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Craft, Discover, and Expand Your Knowledge</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine various materials to create new items and record your discoveries in the dictionary. Will you be able to collect and document every item hidden in the world?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449950/extras/8917802472a00bff60dd4af15f255859.apng?t=1746097092\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449950/extras/8917802472a00bff60dd4af15f255859.poster.avif?t=1746097092\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=153 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Tend to Your Own Farm</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow crops and harvest them with care. Your bounty can be used to learn new skills and craft powerful items.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul>",
